   "source": [
    "# Quick notes about notations\n",
    "\n",
    "## Deriviative\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{df}{dx} = f'(x) = df\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "## Partial deriviative\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{\\partial f}{\\partial x} = f_x(x) = \\partial_x f\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "## Gradient\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\nabla = (\\partial_x f, \\partial_y f,...,\\partial_z f)\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  }
 ],
